## Minimal Usage

CLI:

```bash
boxmot track --detector yolov8n --reid osnet_x0_25_msmt17 --tracker botsort --source video.mp4 --save
```

Python:

```python
from boxmot import Boxmot

run = Boxmot(detector="yolov8n", reid="osnet_x0_25_msmt17", tracker="botsort").track(
    source="video.mp4",
    save=True,
)
print(run)
```

